title: Happy & Healthy with Jeanine Amapola | Trailer
description:
Welcome to the Happy & Healthy Podcast! My hope and goal of this podcast is to simply help and inspire people to be more happy & healthy in all aspects of their lives. Throughout the season, we will be diving deep and getting real and honest about everything from dating, faith, fitness & nutrition,  trending topics and so much more. I will even have a few special guests join in on the journey! I hope you are ready for the wild ride!
